description:
Generate Excalidraw Diagram of Route Planning Architecture

Create a comprehensive Excalidraw diagram that visualizes the application's route planning interface and component structure.

Requirements:
- Map the user interface flow for route planning (input → processing → output)
- Identify and diagram all main components involved in route planning functionality
- Show component hierarchy and relationships (parent-child, sibling interactions)
- Include key data flows between components (props, state, events)
- Highlight external dependencies (APIs, libraries, services)
- Label components with their responsibilities
- Use consistent visual conventions (shapes for component types, arrows for data flow)
- Organize layout for readability (group related components, clear visual hierarchy)

Deliverable:
- Single .excalidraw file with clear, well-organized diagram
- Legend explaining symbols and conventions used
- Sufficient detail for developers to understand the route planning architecture without being cluttered
title: Generate route planning architecture diagram
